### 获取所有课表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/schedules
Content-Type: application/json

### 根据班级ID获取课表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/schedules/class/CLASS_TEST
Content-Type: application/json

### 根据教室ID获取课表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/schedules/classroom/ROOM_TEST
Content-Type: application/json

### 添加课表
POST http://localhost:8080/api/schedules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "classId": "CLASS_TEST",
  "classroomId": "ROOM_TEST",
  "week": 1,
  "weekday": 1,
  "periods": 2
}

### 更新课表
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/schedules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "classId": "CLASS_TEST",
  "classroomId": "ROOM_TEST",
  "week": 1,
  "weekday": 2,
  "periods": 2
}

### 删除课表
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/schedules?classId=CLASS_TEST&week=1&weekday=1&periods=2
Content-Type: application/json
